query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('complex-integration',
'floor-function',
'gcd-and-lcm',
'limits-without-lhopital',
'mathematical-modeling',
'quantifiers',
'spectral-theory',
'supremum-and-infimum',
'topological-groups',
'volume')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1 group by t1.name;
